race.description: Ladbrokes Community Sports Series Maiden Plate
race.comment: AGADOO (9) is an interesting runner who was heavily bet on debut on the Sunshine Coast and after getting back to last made good late ground. Spelled again and resumes here in easier company and leading rider aboard. The rating from his debut run augers well for this, despite finishing 10th. Watch the market closely. GUBER (1) was safely held fresh then ran a much better race here last time when runner-up. Never seems to draw a gate but has good pace and will take catching. GLADDING (5) showed ability in two runs in first campaign including a near miss at Launceston before a spell. Recent trial winner who has good speed and expected to feature fresh. REBEL'S GIRL (7) was well in the market on debut and turned in a forgive run after playing up before the race. Spelled and unbeaten in two trials since. Worth another try. OUT OF THE SPHERE (4) wasn't beaten far at last run before a break and should give a sight fresh.
